rComments: Powerpoints are posted online, but she adds a lot more in class which is crucial for tests. Midterm and exam were tough but if you read the textbook and go to class, you'll be good.

Lots of work for a first year class. The projects are quite time consuming, so don't take this class as a bird, take it if you're genuinely interested or else it won't be worth your time. Her exams are super fair, she's extremely approachable and made this class enjoyable for me. I would definitely take another ADM class with Ghazzawi if I could!
